    "text": "EAGLES Act of 2018\n\nThis bill provides statutory authority for the National Threat Assessment Center (NTAC) within the Department of Homeland Security.\n\nIt authorizes the functions of NTAC through FY2022 and expands them to include the establishment of a national program on targeted school violence prevention."
